recon-ng - to start from terminal 
show workspaces
workspaces add facebook - to add facebook 
use netcraft 
  > set source facebook.com
show options
run
show hosts - to display findings in a good way
use resolve - to list recons
use recon/hosts-hosts/resolve - get ip
run - again to populate ip
use freegeoip - to get location
run - again to populate locations
use report
use reporting/html
set CREATOR name
set CUSTOMER name
set FILENAME /location
run - to export 
